I looked at the final report on Intelligent Transformation in Government Services, which we set up for two years to complete http://t.co/vuRquFKSIw
The Intelligent Turnover ratio was 96.3% in 41 federal agencies and 337 major government services used by dealers on a daily basis. Thank you to all government employees

Working teams succeeded in the transformation of the past two years and the next phase of connecting services and raise the quality of applications and achieve high satisfaction rates http://t.co/al90zwvp27
The two years were not a sword on the shoulders of the teams, but rather a normal administrative and leadership exercise to set a timetable for each ambition and set a time limit for each goal
We set a new goal by reducing the percentage of auditors to all our government centers by 80% until 2018 everyone has the right to complete transactions from his home and through his smartphone
The measure of our success is in providing people's times and facilitating their lives. I tell service center managers your success in reducing people's review of you
